---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import me from "../../public/me.jpeg";
---

<Layout>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif">About Me</h1>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 mt-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-1 order-2 md:order-1">
      <Image
        src={me}
        alt="Marit van der Loos"
        width={1000}
        class="object-cover w-full h-auto max-h-[800px]"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="prose md:col-span-2 order-1 md:order-2">
      <p>
        I am Marit van der Loos, a Creative Technology student based in Utrecht.
        In my studies at the University of Twente, I explore innovative ways to
        use technology, finding creative solutions to relevant problems. I love
        learning about technology and its role in society, designing products,
        making prototypes, and testing them with users. 
        <br>
        <br>
        Before my current studies, I completed the first year of the Bachelorâ€™s in Illustration at
        the Hogeschool voor de Kunsten Utrecht. This experience taught me to
        look at art in new ways, and helped shape my identity as an artist. 
        <br>
        <br>
        In my projects, I love combining art and technology, connecting the
        analogue and digital worlds through a multidisciplinary approach. With
        my work, I want to make a positive impact by creating sustainable
        designs that help people or make them think. 
        <br>
        <br>
        In my free time, I express myself creatively through drawing, painting, knitting, crochet and more.
        Take a look at a selection of my projects on this website!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif">Contact Me</h1>
    <p>You can contact me at vdlmarit(at)gmail(dotcom)</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
